sec.p:
The wn and wp update steps separate out and are iteratively updated until convergence. The wp update step has a simple closed form solution given by the equation:




wpk=median(cpk);wherecpk={wjk|j∈C(p)}



Where wpk is the kth term of the label-p weight vector. cpk is a set of the kth terms of the weight vectors of all the subclasses the label p spans.
